{"tid":1368681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"727嗰日千祈唔好亂咁勇武","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:06:20.000Z","uid":290733,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ada6cae4e565b27eafbac4fd140603e58bdaf3e9","tid":1368681,"uid":290733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"我知我係p 牌仔 但係呢樣野我點都要講 <br />\n<br />\n大家勇武之前請諗一諗自己嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的</span>係啲咩<br />\n<br />\n我哋最終嘅目的係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span>同埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋今次入去只要係為咗係唔好俾啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鄉黑阻住圍村入邊嘅人出嚟發夢</span><br />\n<br />\n記住我哋嘅目標唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">復仇</span>   （復仇清算呢啲野可以等我哋贏咗呢場仗之後再慢慢做）<br />\n<br />\n同埋而家難得政府同警隊自己割蓆，我哋應該將個矛頭指返去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警隊</span></span>嗰邊<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">警隊嘅制度冇失效</span>嘅話，元朗嘅廝殺列車根本冇可能發生<br />\n<br />\n謹記，如果今次我哋做得太過勇武，我哋好容易會<span style=\"color: red;\">失去淺黃個班人嘅支持</span>，亦都會俾<span style=\"color: red;\">政府有一個喘息嘅空間</span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好因為一時的怒火而忘記我哋嘅目的 ：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以希望前線嘅手足勇武之前要諗一諗點解要勇武，唔好為咗勇武而勇武。<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n同埋小心鄕黑搧風點火，栽贓嫁禍"},{"pid":"46855fa1083b77295cc88911d43d31bdbcb7d8ed","tid":1368681,"uid":290733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6da009f26791deb070e1c69c7374f10059e497ce","tid":1368681,"uid":269655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96df32ba246b52933f7e8b16554d68dc53034dc8","tid":1368681,"uid":224829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebc7d0c3829b1399918113e398aedb9da8fe7568","tid":1368681,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得咩叫 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368654</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1adbc7481820e23651464123252d9c5b1e6ba07","tid":1368681,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64737bf55543ab3e3f6a7f2731d644455a7d3820","tid":1368681,"uid":242109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"526a0ad1603fc459bee36db3e73644ddab63e1f0","tid":1368681,"uid":282202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c41d0afdb1900522a4dcc74bee056da3d796d364","tid":1368681,"uid":33623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"前線唔係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8fc24f4f189efceb00e419887264f56e696b03","tid":1368681,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"暫時未見過勇武 &lsquo;亂&lsquo;喎"},{"pid":"c7ebd2a7e0756a2e0486e06c9e121f0fa9f91362","tid":1368681,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"搞佢條村不如搞佢地d酒吧竹館"},{"pid":"023fd42ef6d6fe20ea474b2781c0efc81072f6bd","tid":1368681,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不傷及無辜</span>"},{"pid":"c1a26a42c5a00db7fc11b4fd4c66cf13c013b868","tid":1368681,"uid":17907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"唔入村唔入村唔入村<br />\n敵不動我不動"},{"pid":"f4c91dc349e88281c3479b2fb72de7c5b4f5af1d","tid":1368681,"uid":290733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"我只係想提醒返前線嘅兄弟 依家民意喺